ur drink yet, please pick it up at the drink bar!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event253-02-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"Drink bar is this way.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event253-02-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"Huh, Marina-san!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event253-02-048","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"Fufu, you said you were going to do something fun, so I'm here to help. Leave it to me to support Ririko-san!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event253-02-049","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"Wow, thank you very much! Does it look like everyone's ready to go? ... ahem!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event253-02-050","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"Hey everyone! Today is the sakura party hosted by RiNG, so let's enjoy it as much as we can! Cheers!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event253-02-051","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"All","body":"Cheers!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event253-02-052","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"Saya","body":"You can sit anywhere on the sheets! If you run out of drinks or snacks, please call out to Kasumi or me! We'll go to RiNG to get them!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"event253-02-053","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"Well then, let's get started with the sakura party!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event253-02-054","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"All","body":"Oh, yeah!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event253-02-055","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"Let's see... There she is! Aya-san, is it okay if I sit here?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event253-02-056","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Go ahead! ... Oh, you know my name? It's probably our first time meeting right?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nnf_left01","expressionName":"smile02","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event253-02-057","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"You're Aya-san from Pastel*Palettes, right? And also Chisato-san over here. I see you all on TV!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"smile02","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event253-02-058","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Well, thank you.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event253-02-059","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"Wow, you are totally more beautiful than you look on TV~! Both of you have tiny faces!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"kandou01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event253-02-060","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Eh, do you think so~?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event253-02-061","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Aya-chan, your grin is showing through.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event253-02-062","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"Kanon","body":"Fufu. But it makes me happy to see a Pastel*Palettes fan girl too. I'm Kanon Matsubara, a drummer at Hello, Happy World!. Nice to meet you.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event253-02-063","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Kanon-chan is sharing a room with Chisato-chan!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event253-02-064","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"Sharing a room with a celebrity!? Oh, could it be that Kanon-san is a celebrity too?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event253-02-065","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectRe